t: "√ëalnde O Moo…ìitoyta …ìe denndaangal : \"Ko onon yo onon yo dental jinna, gom…óii on …óu…ó…óinorii (majjingol) yim…ìe …ìen\". Yi…ó…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen ka yim…ìe wi'a : \"Joomi amen, yoga amen dakmitorii yoga, men yottike ngal caatal=lajal amen ngal saatinan…óaa men\". O Daala : \"Ko Yiite ngen woni werde mon, ko on luttoo…ìe ton, si wanaa kon ko Alla Muuyi\". Pellet, Joomi maa…óa ko √ëee√±u…óo, Anndu…óo"